"{\"uid\": \"standard.co.uk-sport-sport-olympics-olympics-2024-matt-hudson-smith-mens-400m-final-b1175162.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"To use the search feature, we need your consent to load Google Custom Search, which may use cookies or similar technologies.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 124, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 56, \"end\": 76, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Google Custom Search\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Please click 'Allow and Continue' below to enable search.\", \"from\": 125, \"to\": 182, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"See our privacy policy for more information.\", \"from\": 183, \"to\": 227, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sport|Olympics  Noah Lylesjokes that the patch of carpet from his bathroom to the spare bedroom of his home is still wet from the stintMatt Hudson-Smithspent living with him.\", \"from\": 229, \"to\": 403, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The world's fastest man was perpetually perplexed by the British 400metre runner's penchant for never drying his feet after a shower, how fine he cut it time wise to make practice and his generally carefree attitude.\", \"from\": 405, \"to\": 621, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 462, \"end\": 469, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9190450049990107, \"rank\": 0.08497687590959202, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Lyles is also adamant Hudson-Smith is so good he will end up being knighted by the king one day.\", \"from\": 623, \"to\": 723, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 627, \"end\": 632, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\", \"score\": 0.9409274288979625, \"rank\": 0.06276087876145789, \"text\": \"Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The pair seem like perhaps unlikely former housemates but, come Wednesday, Hudson-Smith is aiming to emulateLyles as an Olympic champion.\", \"from\": 725, \"to\": 862, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"While Lyles is focused on repeating the sprint treble he achieved at last year's World Athletics Championships in Budapest, Hudson-Smith is adamant his occasional training partner is no sort of inspiration.\", \"from\": 864, \"to\": 1070, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 945, \"end\": 974, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics_Championships\", \"score\": 0.9997860894624495, \"rank\": 0.00015972704650357939, \"text\": \"World Athletics Championships\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics_Championships\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics_Championships\"}, {\"begin\": 978, \"end\": 986, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"score\": 0.998352841918192, \"rank\": 0.0016498756872134735, \"text\": \"Budapest\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"His success does not actually inspire me in the slightest as I inspire myself,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1072, \"to\": 1161, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He has his own mission as do I.\", \"from\": 1162, \"to\": 1194, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"What he is doing is good but I want to emulate my own success.\\\"\", \"from\": 1195, \"to\": 1258, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For his part, Lyles is adamant his former lodger is a shoo-in for the gold and yet he seems both bemused and amused by him.\", \"from\": 1260, \"to\": 1383, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1274, \"end\": 1279, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\", \"score\": 0.9409274288979625, \"rank\": 0.06276087876145789, \"text\": \"Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's funny,\\\" said the American.\", \"from\": 1385, \"to\": 1417, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1408, \"end\": 1416, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9997773804722259, \"rank\": 0.00020716268075829296, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not know if he's told anybody yet but I remember when he was like, 'as soon as I have won a medal, I am retiring'.\", \"from\": 1418, \"to\": 1538, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When is Matt Hudson-Smith running in the men's 400m final at the Olympics 2024 today?\", \"from\": 1540, \"to\": 1625, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Olympics 2024 medal table and latest count today  Olympics 2024: Every Team GB medal winner at the Paris Games so far  \\\"He won a medal two years ago and he's still going so I am hoping that he gets knighted and I get to see him get knighted.\", \"from\": 1627, \"to\": 1868, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sir Matthew Hudson-Smith.\\\"\", \"from\": 1869, \"to\": 1895, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1873, \"end\": 1893, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matthew_Hudson-Smith\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Matthew Hudson-Smith\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matthew_Hudson-Smith\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matthew_Hudson-Smith\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hudson-Smith has looked imperious this season, even more so here in Paris where he ripped the field apart in the opening 70m and was never troubled,easing up halfway down the straight to win his semi-final.\", \"from\": 1897, \"to\": 2103, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1965, \"end\": 1970, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 4.602769077723178e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He did not stop to talk to the media post-race, instead simply wagging a finger and laughing.\", \"from\": 2105, \"to\": 2198, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Many are ready to place the gold around his neck already at the2024 Olympicsand the athlete himself is well aware of his pre-race favourite tag.\", \"from\": 2200, \"to\": 2344, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"To his rivals, he said simply, \\\"If you want to win it, you have got to take it [the gold] from me.\", \"from\": 2345, \"to\": 2443, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am ready.\\\"\", \"from\": 2444, \"to\": 2456, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A gold to follow that ofKeely Hodgkinson in the 800mwould be historic making him the first British male to do so since Eric Liddell, of Chariots of Fire fame, to do so exactly 100 years ago in the same city.\", \"from\": 2458, \"to\": 2665, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2488, \"end\": 2498, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\", \"score\": 0.7639463803246748, \"rank\": 0.3089923923388531, \"text\": \"Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\"}, {\"begin\": 2577, \"end\": 2589, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eric_Liddell\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.398414229211037e-46, \"text\": \"Eric Liddell\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eric_Liddell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eric_Liddell\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Of that potential for history making, Hudson-Smith said simply: \\\"It's one step at a time.\", \"from\": 2667, \"to\": 2756, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am very much a person who is present right now.\", \"from\": 2757, \"to\": 2806, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have got to take care of the now and then I look to the future and take care of everything.\\\"\", \"from\": 2807, \"to\": 2901, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Gold would cap a remarkable journey, his career littered with injuries and following the admission when he won his first World Championship medal in 2022 that he had previously attempted to commit suicide.\", \"from\": 2903, \"to\": 3108, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Key figures have helped to rebuild him from his coach Gary Evans to another former Olympic champion for the distance, Christine Ohuruogu, who is constantly in his ear to advise and reassure.\", \"from\": 3110, \"to\": 3300, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3164, \"end\": 3174, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gary_Evans_(golfer)\", \"score\": 0.9404359203211077, \"rank\": 0.03333333333334321, \"text\": \"Gary Evans\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13156709\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gary_Evans_(golfer)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gary_Evans_(golfer)\"}, {\"begin\": 3228, \"end\": 3246, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christine_Ohuruogu\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Christine Ohuruogu\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christine_Ohuruogu\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christine_Ohuruogu\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The combination of voices is clearly working as he has slashed half a second off his personal best already this season and, going into the final, intimates he can run quicker yet.\", \"from\": 3302, \"to\": 3481, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You know after 2021 when that reality check did hit,\\\" he said looking back on the darker days, \\\"I had a lot of talks and people basically saying to me 'it's time to take the sport seriously'.\", \"from\": 3483, \"to\": 3675, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I watched a podcast with Michael Johnson and he was saying that you do things not because you like it but because you have to do it.\", \"from\": 3677, \"to\": 3810, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3703, \"end\": 3718, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Johnson_(sprinter)\", \"score\": 0.6562406956374156, \"rank\": 0.2753288987434648, \"text\": \"Michael Johnson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Johnson_(sprinter)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Johnson_(sprinter)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There are no real excuses.\", \"from\": 3811, \"to\": 3837, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I used to avoid the gym like the plague.\", \"from\": 3838, \"to\": 3878, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's been a long road but I think maturity, growth and being a total overall athlete has allowed me to be the best version of myself.\", \"from\": 3880, \"to\": 4014, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Now, the results are showing.\\\"\", \"from\": 4015, \"to\": 4045, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"MORE ABOUT  Have your say...  1  Crime  Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line train after youths told to stop vaping by middle-aged passenger  Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line after youths told to stop vaping  2  Football  Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup, confirmed team news, injury latest for Premier League today  Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup and confirmed team news  3  UK  Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning over Donald Trump